snippet.title: Curse of the Crescent Isle DX Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for my upcoming game "Curse of the Crescent Isle DX". 
Graphics by Michael Lambert, Music Arranged by Steve Lakawicz, Music Composed by Daniel Davis, Designed and Programmed by Adam Mowery, Cover Art by Temmie Chang. Thanks for everyone's support and feedback! Please vote for it on Steam Greenlight here:
